{"tid":1360162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[727]  元朗記者會分析+解讀，遊行策略應對","createTime":"2019-07-24T09:48:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T12:01:33.000Z","uid":231905,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fe8fecfe62b98351795b8390b917567cbae91a41","tid":1360162,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:48:23.000Z","msg":"記者會 link: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vE__Sh7lMDA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvE__Sh7lMDA&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9RR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=3ab57879\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vE__Sh7lMDA</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">5:40-6:20</span>  <br />\n提到721同近期暴力事件，令元朗居民對727遊行感到憂慮，擔心暴力事件發生<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">解讀</span>：將和平示威遊行同暴力掛勾，渲染遊行搞亂香港論。同時強調元朗居民，暗地煽動保家衛族情緒。<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">6:20-7:04</span>  <br />\n指出如果遊行成事，請和平進行。希望遊行可以和平進行，同時希望鄉民保持克制，避免不必要衝突。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">解讀</span>：對和平遊行釋出善意，意味遊行可搞。暗示鄉民會收斂，唔會主動出手。<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">7:04-7:20</span>  <br />\n反對一切非法暴力，希望政府同各方對話，化解矛盾<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">解讀</span>：推波比政府，唔想上身<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">7:20-7:40</span>  <br />\n香港是我家，唔想社會撕裂，唔想因政見不同出現暴力，愛元朗，反暴力。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">解讀</span>：首尾呼應，同第一段一樣<br />\n[blue7:40-8:00[/blue]  <br />\n煮豆燃豆萁，豆在釜中泣，本是同根生，相煎何太急<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">解讀</span>：冇咩好解<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">成段聲明，重點係呢段</span></span><br />\n指出如果遊行成事，請和平進行。希望遊行可以和平進行，同時希望鄉民保持克制，避免不必要衝突。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">解讀</span>：對和平遊行釋出善意，意味遊行可搞。暗示鄉民會收斂，唔會主動出手。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">遊行方向</span></span><br />\n所以當日遊行，必需和理非進行，當然勇武自衛亦必需。<br />\n我方應同樣釋出善意，針對警黑，逼面果浸鄉紳名義上同黑社會割蓆<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以比鄉黑擔正「保家衛族」大旗。</span><br />\n<br />\n727 元朗見"},{"pid":"db505214068d465ef7ef8c5e9721372f9228785f","tid":1360162,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:49:26.000Z","msg":"唔可以比班元朗佬講中我地去搞事"},{"pid":"2482cd28ab4d93a38518427f2223b7345c81c67c","tid":1360162,"uid":231905,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:50:23.000Z","msg":"只要「保家衛族」大旗一扶正<br />\n以後大西北手足都會仆街"},{"pid":"b129707ed03248094b309293c8d73b7ab59e82f8","tid":1360162,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:50:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"62b9d5a5eed867358fe8a889e0c4cd9c8964582d","tid":1360162,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:51:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7d6375858cedd97caf79c7aae2388f5546ae17d2","tid":1360162,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:51:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"355aa8e74a53b66282f3202fe3cdd6c9af9d333b","tid":1360162,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:51:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5cd081d2564bfd5300535115d118435cc7a41dc5","tid":1360162,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:51:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a95aeaf505e26fdffaf7ec8d9a02e3edd0c570be","tid":1360162,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:52:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"10401a10a3b3678be3903c04244f4cba7c7d4472","tid":1360162,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:52:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5ec95a41882e7b94fd3bcad60c1327e64b26205c","tid":1360162,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:52:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9087a13bb40829f808687783e99c6656d2aef6f0","tid":1360162,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:53:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"aad17c17d0a56d253e934fb8b90e2306fa471bb8","tid":1360162,"uid":231905